****Story****
Once upon a time, In a forest, THere a lived a monkey who recided on a berry tree, Which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day, Crocodile came to the banks of a river, and rested under a tree. The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the nextday for more friuts, As he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and monkey became good friends.
By 
Vedant Varande.
